{"tid":139950,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"<AM730> 猶太人和香港警察最會賺錢","createTime":"2017-03-01T23:12:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-01T23:47:36.000Z","uid":35790,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a5cce583d04d88830d6d1dd93c0cdb8a97c2eef7","tid":139950,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T23:12:14.000Z","msg":"猶太人和香港警察最會賺錢(節錄) <br />\n<br />\n不計醫、法等專科，普通一個大學畢業生只有一萬多元、不足兩萬元的平均月薪。然而，警務人員起薪點高達39,660至42,110元。如大學畢業直接投考督察，起薪點為40,880元，即使普通警員的薪酬也遠超一般大學生，月薪22,410元。如此筍工，我真的不知道哪兒找。這也難怪沈智慧會講：「警察唔係免費服務社會㗎！They are well paid for it！」 警察真係好好paid，也難怪警察會覺得自己跟搵錢能力極高的猶太人睇成一線。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.am730.com.hk/column/財經/猶太人和香港警察最會賺錢-68031\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.am730.com.hk%2Fcolumn%2F%E8%B2%A1%E7%B6%93%2F%E7%8C%B6%E5%A4%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%92%8C%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F%E6%9C%80%E6%9C%83%E8%B3%BA%E9%8C%A2-68031&d=MMgAXMBwwZFGDPTkcL6JsW6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=d59e8381\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.am730.com.hk/column/財經/猶太人和香港警察最會賺錢-68031</a>(全文)"},{"pid":"60110198a4628bd7e8749007652c9d05e9586827","tid":139950,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T23:12:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbf1989b2a7cdab89b0fdf85e54209e55f129c9a","tid":139950,"uid":42767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T23:18:12.000Z","msg":"站在忠黨愛國的立場，我很痛心，身為中國人的警察竟然自認猶太人。香港警察竟然背祖忘宗，崇猶媚外。我建議政府不單要提升警察的愛國水平，更要延至其家眷及子女，多搞一些北上愛國營，進行思想再教育，好讓偉大毛主席的思想教誨深入其每一寸皮膚骨骼，明白太陽紅的美好，認清歷史，記住他們才是中國人，他們應共享做中國人的榮耀。"},{"pid":"c912e056192bf8b3050b3ea02067b90ef2374ab6","tid":139950,"uid":54264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T23:23:19.000Z","msg":"猶差冇得輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/superman.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b606f984f532c9dacffe9dad9531b2bb5b66c34","tid":139950,"uid":34834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T23:28:36.000Z","msg":"shylock<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff2780626aa7c0eca31a2e58df5de3b646f975bb","tid":139950,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T23:44:33.000Z","msg":"警員起薪高過polyu 3寶起薪"},{"pid":"e030b75ccdf693d866a2b2addc9fe4ad0ae53a5b","tid":139950,"uid":20554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T23:47:36.000Z","msg":"我地班納稅黨真係賤過地底泥"}]}